  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1938, February the 16th-- I remember that day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the beginning, naturally, we was training, and training [? all ?] kind of like any soldier.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, like my profession is a, a blacksmith.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they need a blacksmith.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took me as a, as a blacksmith.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the blacksmith shop, in the army blacksmith shop.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I wasn't-- there was two kind of blacksmiths around there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Was blacksmith what they used to shoe horses and blacksmiths what they used to do all kinds of work what they needed-- no horses.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that-- I was doing that kind of work, wagon repairs, person, all kind of whatever, anything what they need to do.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Depend-- mostly all day, [? about ?] eight hours, seven hours, something like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Shabbos, no-- we, we used to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Shabbos wasn't any holiday.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now when was a holiday, like a big holiday, like Rosh Hashanah, Yom Kippur, or Shavuot, or Pesach, they used take us, the Jewish soldiers, to a, to a synagogue, and then, like Pesach, to a kosher kitchen.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They used to give us meals.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The kosher kitchen was located close to [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Eishyshok, ?] like in [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Villna. ?] And we used to hear pretty good speakers and very good [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mostly, one time was speaking a Jewish captain, a Jewish captain from the, from the army.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was speaking in Polish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said, on our shoulders is all the Judaism exist.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because some people was complaining they were taking the Jewish people in the army, the discrimination, everything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when he brought it out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He said openly, exactly, or [? we were ?] supposed to glad they are take us to the army.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think on [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Shavuot. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
